title: Sally Voltaire & Systrar
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, European, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Busy deli / lunch restaurant in the Ahlens department store. Each day offers a fish dish plus 2 or 3 veggie ones like salads and sometimes a soup. A shop selling ecological skincare and kitchen products is attached.
